NAME
    Bot::Cobalt::Plugin::Silly - Silly Bot::Cobalt plugins

DESCRIPTION
    A collection of completely silly Bot::Cobalt plugins; these can be add
    to your `plugins.conf' to do very useless stuff.

    In fact, most of them don't even do useless stuff on their own, but
    rather bridge other stuff that does useless stuff.

    For an added bonus, they're all hastily-written, too!

    *   Bot::Cobalt::Plugin::Silly::AutoOpAll AutoOp *all* users that join a
        channel.

    *   Bot::Cobalt::Plugin::Silly::DailyFail Enlightening newspaper
        headlines; bridges Acme::Daily::Fail

    *   Bot::Cobalt::Plugin::Silly::LOLCAT Bridge <POE::Filter::LOLCAT> to
        translate text into LOLCAT

    *   Bot::Cobalt::Plugin::Silly::OutputLOLCAT LOLCAT-enabled bot output
        filter

    *   Bot::Cobalt::Plugin::Silly::OutputAngryGerman Loud German output
        filter (similar to Acme::LAUTER::DEUTSCHER)

    *   Bot::Cobalt::Plugin::Silly::OutputLeet Leetspeak output filter
        (bridges Acme::LeetSpeak)

    *   Bot::Cobalt::Plugin::Silly::MstOMatic Get Matt S. Trout rants on
        demand. (In appreciation for bringing us Moo, of course)

    *   Bot::Cobalt::Plugin::Silly::Reverse Reverse a string.

    *   Bot::Cobalt::Plugin::Silly::Rot13 Rot13 a string.

    *   Bot::Cobalt::Plugin::Silly::ThreatLevel Get the current DHS terror
        alert level, so you know when to duct tape your house shut.

CONTRIBUTING
    I'd be happy to review contributed Silly plugins to potentially add more
    uselessness to this distribution.

    Send them off to <avenj@cobaltirc.org>, please.

    The only real requirement is that they not do much of anything anyone
    might find productive.

AUTHOR
    Jon Portnoy <avenj@cobaltirc.org>

    http://www.cobaltirc.org

